'''''Winnie''''', ni filime yerekana ubuzima bwa Sinema yo muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika]] yepfo yasohotse muri 2017 yayobowe na Pascale Lamche ikanakorwa na Christoph Jörg na Steven Markovitz kuri Pumpernickel Films, Submarine Films, Big World Cinema<ref>https://www.imdb.com/title/tt6333082/</ref><ref>https://www.sundance.org/projects/winnie</ref>. 

Iyi filime ivuga ku buzima bwa Winnie Madikizela-Mandela n'urugamba rwe adacogora rwo gukuraho Apartheid muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Epfo. <ref>https://africa.film/winnie-a-pascale-lamche-documentary/</ref>  Iyi filime yerekanwe mu rwego rwo kwerekana iserukiramuco ry'uburenganzira bwa muntu 2019.<ref>https://www.filmplatform.net/product/winnie/</ref>  Muri uwo mwaka, Lamche yatsindiye igihembo cy'umuyobozi mwiza wa documentaire mpuzamahanga mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Sundance .  Yatowe kandi muri Afurika Movie Academy Awards ibihembo bya Documentaire nziza<ref>https://www.pbs.org/independentlens/documentaries/winnie/</ref><ref>https://www.worldcat.org/title/winnie/oclc/989980158</ref>.

